txt.en: Descendants of Beorn have not traditionally left the skin-changer's home-land, but your journey has brought you to Eriador in defence of the Free Peoples. You should now go to meet your cousin Varthmath in Moria, at the Orc-watch in the Redhorn Lodes.
Your journey continues in Moria and Rhovanian.
The Line of Beorn, Part Four
